ESP32:GPIO 21: OLED SDA
GPIO 22: OLED SCL
GPIO 25: Rotary Encoder CLK
GPIO 26: Rotary Encoder DT
GPIO 27: Rotary Encoder SW
GPIO 33: Button 1 (Play/Pause)
GPIO 32: Button 2 (Volume Up)
GPIO 13: Button 3 (Mute)
GPIO 12: Button 4 (Volume Down)
GPIO 5: Button 5 (Record/Device Switch)
GPIO 4: IR LED (via 2N2222)
GPIO 15: IR Receiver OUT
GPIO 34: Battery voltage (via voltage divider)
GPIO 2: Debug LED (onboard)
5V, GND: From DC-DC boost converter

